<h3>What is this project?</h3>
<p>
    The <strong>MSFD Full Stack Solution</strong> is an educational project built with:
</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Backend:</strong> ASP.NET Core Web API that serves product data</li>
    <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Blazor WebAssembly for interactive user interface</li>
</ul>

<h3>Key Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li>RESTful API endpoint for retrieving products</li>
    <li>Product catalog with ID, Name, and Price information</li>
    <li>Real-time data fetching from the backend</li>
    <li>Cross-origin request support (CORS)</li>
    <li>Responsive table display with Bootstrap styling</li>
</ul>

